Blaze.uk.title: The Real Conjuring: Our Story

Blaze.uk.title: The Real Conjuring: Our Story
Blaze.uk.description: Who is Haunting the Old Arnold Estate?: The investigation continues as this horror documentary concludes, aiming to separate The Conjuring's facts from its fiction. (2 of 2)

Blaze.uk.title: Weird Or What? With William Shatner
Blaze.uk.description: Mysterious Vanishings: Baffling stories of people who vanished without a trace, including a young Tasmanian pilot who is chased by unidentified aircraft before disappearing. (S3, ep 8)

Blaze.uk.title: Weird Or What? With William Shatner
Blaze.uk.description: Medical Mysteries: Medics at a hospital fall gravely ill after treating a mysteriously ailing patient in a circumstance that can't be explained by science. Or can it? (S3, ep 9)

Blaze.uk.title: The Unxplained With William Shatner
Blaze.uk.description: Sacred Rituals: Many cultures have used sacred rituals to express their spiritual beliefs throughout human history, with some even thought to unlock supernatural powers. (S3, ep 36)

Blaze.uk.title: The UnXplained...
Blaze.uk.description: Tales of the Tormented: Throughout history, tales of inexplicable maladies have stirred morbid curiosity - from mysterious wounds to a madness that compels people to dance. (S4, ep 5)

Blaze.uk.title: Hardcore Pawn
Blaze.uk.description: Gold Day In Hell: Les discovers Seth's masterplan for a new business structure at the Gold family pawn shop, leading to a huge stand-off between father and son. (S5, ep 13)

Blaze.uk.title: Hardcore Pawn
Blaze.uk.description: Face Off: Tensions are at an all-time high in the store, as Seth and Les jockey for power. As the chaos begins to affect business, Ashley stages an intervention. (S6, ep 1)

Blaze.uk.title: Hardcore Pawn
Blaze.uk.description: Last Man Standing: All eyes are on Seth as he tries to prove he's worthy of the keys to the kingdom. But as business heats up, can he stay calm under the mounting pressure? (S6, ep 2)

Blaze.uk.title: Hardcore Pawn
Blaze.uk.description: Family Traitor: Seth makes a huge mistake that threatens to land the store in financial disaster. As he scrambles to correct it, Ashley spills the beans to Les. (S6, ep 3)

Blaze.uk.title: Hardcore Pawn
Blaze.uk.description: Millionaire Mayhem: Les works at breakneck pace to customise a $20,000 diamond ring. And when Ashley unjustifiably derails the sale, no-one blames Seth for hitting the roof. (S6, ep 4)

Blaze.uk.title: Hardcore Pawn
Blaze.uk.description: Urban Hillbilly: A customer hits the roof after Seth busts him for trying to flog fake goods. Later, panic grips the staff as a farmer lets an animal loose in the shop. (S6, ep 5)

Blaze.uk.title: Auction Hunters
Blaze.uk.description: Tough As Nails: The guys head to a live auction to buy and sell. They uncover an unusual Marilyn Monroe statue, an industrial slip 'n' slide, and a bed of nails. (S5, ep 11)

Blaze.uk.title: Auction Hunters
Blaze.uk.description: New. Missouri Loves Company: On a visit to see Ton's sister in Missouri, the guys hit up a live auction and score a ballista and an anvil set made for an explosive sport. (S5, ep 10)

Blaze.uk.title: Auction Hunters
Blaze.uk.description: Louisiana Purchase: Ton and Allen encounter some salty locals at a shipping crate auction.  After spending a lot of cash, they find a tactical blast shield. (S5, ep 9)

Blaze.uk.title: Auction Hunters
Blaze.uk.description: Party Gras: On a trip to New Orleans, Ton and Allen look to mix business with pleasure, and wage war with some locals at a tough auction. (S5, ep 8)

Blaze.uk.description: ...Henry's Wreck-trospective. The Ardingly Wreck- Trospective: Dive headfirst into the archives to celebrate the very best bits from the hit series Junk & Disorderly. (S1, ep 7)

Blaze.uk.title: Alien Disclosure Files
Blaze.uk.description: The Paradox: As the Fermi Paradox states, the likelihood of advanced life in the universe is surprisingly high - so why haven't we had any contact with extraterrestrial life? (S1, ep 10)

Blaze.uk.title: Alien Disclosure Files
Blaze.uk.description: Physical Evidence: Physical evidence of alien activity has been hidden from the public for years - but it is starting to be revealed. (S1, ep 11)

Blaze.uk.title: Encounter: UFO
Blaze.uk.description: Being on an aircraft that comes in close proximity to an object that doesn't appear on radar is a scary experience. Who are they and what do they want? (S1, ep 4)

Blaze.uk.title: The UnXplained:...
Blaze.uk.description: ...Mysteries of the Universe. Mysterious Earth: Earth remains a mystery to the billions of people on it. How did it come to exist? And how long will humans call it 'home'? (S1, ep 3)

Blaze.uk.title: The Mystery Of The Holy Lance
Blaze.uk.description: Explore the fascinating 2,000-year-long history of the Holy Lance, a sacred relic of Christianity sought by Emperor Constantine, Napoleon Bonaparte and Adolf Hitler.

E4Plus1.uk.description: Waverly Hills, 9-0-2-1-D'oh: The family rent a flat in the affluent Waverly Hills area so that Bart and Lisa can get into a good school. (S20 Ep19/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: I Won't Be Home for Christmas: When Moe convinces Homer to stay out late on Christmas Eve, Marge kicks him out of the house and he has to spend Christmas alone. (S26 Ep9/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Man Who Came to Be Dinner: A new amusement park ride transports the Simpsons to Kang and Kodos's home planet, where they're held captive in a zoo. (S26 Ep10/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Feelings flourish for some couples as Love/Hate Week gets underway. But love languishes and emotions erupt when one groom hears his wife's critiques. (S10 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: MAFS UK: It's Official!...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...With Lucinda Light: Brand new series - Lucinda's joined by Donna Preston. With three commitment ceremonies left, it's make-or-break. And bride Leah chats about causing chaos! (S3 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Virgin Island
E4Plus1.uk.description: As the course approaches its climax, it's time for the group to learn about masturbation and how to have an orgasm. Zac finds out the hard way that sex can be complicated. (Ep5)

SkyMix.uk.description: The Best of Both Worlds - Part 1: The Borg captures Captain Picard after the Enterprise answers a distress call from one of the Federation's most remote colonies. (S3, ep 26)

SkyMix.uk.title: Star Trek: The Next Generation
SkyMix.uk.description: Part two of two. Riker faces a life-or-death decision as the Borg use Picard in a bid to conquer Earth. Sci-fi adventure, starring Patrick Stewart. (S4, Ep 1)

SkyMix.uk.title: Star Trek: The Next Generation
SkyMix.uk.description: Family: Still recovering from his time with the Borg, Picard considers resigning from Starfleet. Worf's parents make an embarrassing trip to the Enterprise. (S4, Ep 2)

SkyMix.uk.title: FILM: The Reluctant Royal
SkyMix.uk.description: When Philly mechanic Johnny learns that his long-lost father is a duke, he reluctantly enters the world of royalty. Starring Emilie de Ravin. (2025)

SkyMix.uk.title: David Attenborough: Micro Monsters
SkyMix.uk.description: Conflict: Sir David Attenborough explores the macroscopic world of bugs and, in this first episode, finds out how its residents outwit their enemies to survive. (Ep 1 of 6)

SkyMix.uk.title: David Attenborough: Micro Monsters
SkyMix.uk.description: Predator: It's a bug-eat-bug world out there, and the documentary continues with a look at how the various critters defuse the defences of their prey. (Ep 2 of 6)

SkyMix.uk.title: Great Barrier Reef With David Attenborough
SkyMix.uk.description: Builders: David Attenborough descends beneath the waves and meets some of the tiny coral animals that helped build the Reef and make it an underwater wonderland. (1 of 3)

SkyMix.uk.title: Age Of The Big Cats
SkyMix.uk.description: Discover the stories of the puma and the leopard. Investigate how they survived the Ice Age, and how they evolved into the fierce predators they are today. (S1, ep 3)

SkyMix.uk.title: Agatha Raisin
SkyMix.uk.description: Agatha Raisin and The Wizard of Evesham: Ashley Jensen returns as super-stylish sleuth Agatha Raisin, and she's sure her Cotswolds hairdresser is up to no good. (S2, ep 1)

SkyMix.uk.title: Agatha Raisin
SkyMix.uk.description: Agatha Raisin and The Wizard of Evesham: The beauty salon case continues for sassy sleuth Agatha as she digs deeper into her charming hair stylist's crimes. (S2, ep 2)

SkyMix.uk.title: Rob & Romesh Vs Usain Bolt
SkyMix.uk.description: Comedian mates Rob Beckett and Romesh Ranganathan head to Jamaica to meet sprint legend Usain Bolt - the fastest man ever to have lived. (S1, ep 1)

SkyMix.uk.title: New: NCIS: New Orleans
SkyMix.uk.description: Illusions: As Pride orders the team to link Sasha to the recent attacks in New Orleans, he must also help Connor come to terms with who his mother really is. (S7, ep 14)

SkyMix.uk.title: New: NCIS: New Orleans
SkyMix.uk.description: Runs in the Family: While Pride and Rita plan their wedding, the FBI try to get Connor's mother by placing him under arrest for the bar's firebombing. (S7, ep 15)
